{"tid":838912,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"息魔殺到︰翠林花園加息後減至446萬沽　重返去年底","createTime":"2018-09-27T13:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T18:19:28.000Z","uid":83582,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0947c8919ec1bfce22732b8d0a54c7a3170258db","tid":838912,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n09月27日(四) 19:05<br />\n<br />\n息魔殺到︰翠林花園加息後減至446萬沽　重返去年底<br />\n<br />\n屯門翠林花園再有「跳樓貨」，美聯高文帆表示，屋苑C座高層C室，實用面積429方呎，上周末才叫價530萬元放盤，受市況影響，昨日(9月26日)已減價至480萬元。<br />\n<br />\n今日香港加息，業主恐樓市會回落，有買家還價446萬元，即時沽出單位，呎價約10,396元，<span style=\"color: red;\">樓價重返去年底水平</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180927/bkn-20180927190527322-0927_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180927%2Fbkn-20180927190527322-0927_00842_001.html&d=QFB8rg%2Bw8BgRi8i1z1WEUPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=284305f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180927/bkn-20180927190527322-0927_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"71e6f520e4dd8a2ac33aba9ed2c55b2a9d977852","tid":838912,"uid":180515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"好過買上源<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da04092d1268e3502f79f7d1eaa5904457e73c49","tid":838912,"uid":51294,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"跌咁少 添D 啦"},{"pid":"1f39a86b2ce30a056314d563ac2e4c0d4dedfc3e","tid":838912,"uid":41944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"高層唔計<br />\n屯門太遠唔計"},{"pid":"077ac3839ab52afcb9c727fb74052b26aeea74c1","tid":838912,"uid":39226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"咁遠唔計啦"},{"pid":"cce019416a5aa89863d9b799a9afdabb0c3dde65","tid":838912,"uid":4826,"like":4,"dislik